OL,3,CCabinet not split over winter fuel
OL,4,Cpayment cut, Downing Street insists
OL,6,FDowning Street has insisted that Sir
OL,7,FKeir Starmer's Cabinet is "united"
OL,8,Fbehind plans to cut winter fuel
OL,9,Fpayments for millions of pensioners
OL,10,Famid a backlash over the policy.
OL,12,FThere have been calls from some union
OL,13,Fleaders for the government to U-turn
OL,14,Fon its decision, which will see all
OL,15,Fbut the country's poorest pensioners
OL,16,Fstripped of the winter fuel payment.
OL,18,FThere have even been calls within
OL,19,FLabour ranks for the government to
OL,20,Fsoften the policy, ahead of Tuesday's
OL,21,FCommons vote.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
