OL,4,Cpayment cut, Downing Street insists
OL,6,FHowever, a Number 10 spokeswoman said
OL,7,Fministers "agreed" on the importance
OL,8,Fof "fixing the foundations of the
OL,9,Feconomy" by making tough and unpopular
OL,10,Fspending decisions.
OL,12,F"The Prime Minister opened Cabinet by
OL,13,Fstating the importance of fixing the
OL,14,Ffoundations of our economy in order to
OL,15,Fcarry out the Government's mandate for
OL,16,Fchange," the spokeswoman said.
