OL,4,Cpayment cut, Downing Street insists
OL,6,F"He said that, given the scale of
OL,7,Finheritance, this would be difficult
OL,8,Fand that tough decisions are unpopular
OL,9,Fdecisions, but it is the tough
OL,10,Fdecisions that will enable change for
OL,11,Fthis country."
OL,13,FDame Diana Johnson, the policing
OL,14,Fminister, suggested Monday that
OL,15,Fministers were looking at how the
OL,16,Fdecision to scrap the payments for 10
OL,17,Fmillion pensioners could be softened.
