OL,4,Cpayment cut, Downing Street insists
OL,6,FHowever, Treasury sources said she
OL,7,F"misspoke" in suggesting the
OL,8,Fgovernment is looking at doing more
OL,9,Fthan encouraging further take-up of
OL,10,Fpension credit.
OL,12,FThere was no discussion of softening
OL,13,Fthe impact of the winter fuel cut at
OL,14,FCabinet on Monday, Downing Street said.
OL,16,FAsked whether Dame Diana Johnson had
OL,17,Fbeen "freelancing" when she said
OL,18,Fmitigations were being looked at by
OL,19,Fministers, a No 10 spokeswoman said:
OL,20,F"I think it was promptly corrected."
