OL,4,Cpayment cut, Downing Street insists
OL,6,FUnder the plans announced by
OL,7,FChancellor Rachel Reeves in July,
OL,8,Fwinter fuel payments will be
OL,9,Frestricted to those receiving pension
OL,10,Fcredit, meaning millions of pensioners
OL,11,Fwill lose out on payments of between
OL,12,F#200 and #300 this winter.
OL,14,FSeventeen Labour MPs have now signed a
OL,15,Fmotion put forward by Neil Duncan-
OL,16,FJordan, one of the parliamentary
OL,17,Fparty's newly elected members, calling
OL,18,Fon the government to delay
OL,19,Fimplementing the cut.
