OL,4,Cpayment cut, Downing Street insists
OL,6,FThe motion has also been signed by six
OL,7,Fof the seven Labour MPs who lost the
OL,8,Fwhip in July after voting against the
OL,9,FKing's Speech over the government's
OL,10,Frefusal to abolish the two-child
OL,11,Fbenefit cap.
OL,13,FHowever, ministers continue to insist
OL,14,Fthe cut is necessary to help fill a
OL,15,F#22 billion "black hole" in this
OL,16,Fyear's budget, left by their
OL,17,FConservative predecessors.
