OL,10,FUnion leaders have criticised
OL,11,FStarmer's plans, with Rail, Maritime
OL,12,Fand Transport (RMT) union general
OL,13,Fsecretary Mick Lynch saying the
OL,14,Fgovernment is making a "historic
OL,15,Fmistake".
OL,17,F"They will have to do something about
OL,18,Fthis historic mistake, otherwise we
OL,19,Fwill start to see the consequences
OL,20,Fthis winter," he told a fringe meeting
